Multimodal Model Architecture: Four Encoders -> Fusion -> Decoder. Text -> Tokenizer, Image -> Vision Encoder, Audio -> Audio Encoder, Video -> Video Encoder. All project to shared representation space. Fusion Encoder combines. Decoder (LLM) generates output. Model cards: GPT-4o, Claude 4 Vision, Gemini 2.5 Pro, Llama 4 90B with modalities, resolution, price. German labels, clean architecture diagram.